// User Guide: Fusion Runtime Core v3.0 "Supernova"1. Getting StartedInstallationAdd Supernova to your Cargo.toml. Note the distinct lack of tokio.[dependencies]
// fusion-rt-core = { version = "3.0", features = ["gpu", "qpu", "wasm", "distributed"] }
// Basic Runtime SetupSupernova requires explicit configuration of the hardware backend.use fusion_rt_core::prelude::*;
